    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/6d9403532a73bd29befc4e38a1032066.avif?t=1678440394\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>故事发生在阴暗且视野不良的废弃医院。<br>能够依靠的只有一支手电筒，以及微光的蜡烛。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/4e2f1d97380e70b9359dac5c48833daf.poster.avif?t=1678440394\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/4e2f1d97380e70b9359dac5c48833daf.webm?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/4e2f1d97380e70b9359dac5c48833daf.mp4?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>然而在这医院里...有着一群会袭击冬花的...鬼魂们。<br>这里有着不用光线照亮就看不到真身的，潜影黑暗之鬼―――<br>又或是能听见任何细微声音的，隐密气息之鬼―――<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/67ef9d03526c481317b22c07f9e1e63c.poster.avif?t=1678440394\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/67ef9d03526c481317b22c07f9e1e63c.webm?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/67ef9d03526c481317b22c07f9e1e63c.mp4?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>本作将带给玩家在废医院探索时，被出鬼没袭击的恐怖体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/89eaa1596009eddcaec674c0c31729cd.avif?t=1678440394\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>如果见到了鬼魂，请尽速「逃离」。<br>逃跑的勇气正是逃出医院的唯一法则。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/e4ae0b56b412e776e69bdb71f44a6467.poster.avif?t=1678440394\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/e4ae0b56b412e776e69bdb71f44a6467.webm?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/e4ae0b56b412e776e69bdb71f44a6467.mp4?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>闪避追逐的鬼时，可以善用医院地形、储物柜、以及使用道具。<br>探索中可以获得的道具，有能照亮道路的蜡烛，又或是可以直接妨碍鬼的道具...等。<br>根据使用方法可以派上很大的帮助！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/549620cc9227f53496e75f9ff400cb92.avif?t=1678440394\" width=616 height=70 /></span><br>废弃医院里，可以获得四散各地的绘图日记。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/1db5b71c8c3d95dd35d724bf3b307c81.poster.avif?t=1678440394\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/1db5b71c8c3d95dd35d724bf3b307c81.webm?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1675620/extras/1db5b71c8c3d95dd35d724bf3b307c81.mp4?t=1678440394\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>这些绘图日记是记载着医院过去血案的唯一线索。<br>同时，随着游戏每一轮难度的提升，<br>对剧情的不解以及期望，也将在最后一步一步导向无限的绝望。",
